25
00:01:50,910 --> 00:01:51,780
it would've followed

26
00:01:52,030 --> 00:01:53,220
a parabolic arc
and landed on Zhou Shiyun.

27
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:54,450
We all know that

28
00:01:54,910 --> 00:01:55,780
