49
00:02:42,710 --> 00:02:43,220
Mr. Fu,

50
00:02:43,550 --> 00:02:44,460
I'll head back now.

51
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:51,970
Gu explained everything thoroughly,

52
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:52,570
didn't she?

53
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:54,740
We'll also reserve our right

54
00:02:55,040 --> 00:02:55,940
to pursue legal action

55
00:02:56,110 --> 00:02:57,780
for slander and those things.

56
