Let us know if there is any news.

57
00:02:59,520 --> 00:02:59,810
Let's go.

58
00:03:01,830 --> 00:03:02,370
Oh, by the way,

59
00:03:02,870 --> 00:03:04,620
you all have my card, right?

60
00:03:05,430 --> 00:03:06,300
Big projects, no sweat,

61
