I promise

72
00:03:21,320 --> 00:03:22,650
I'll handle it properly.

73
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:23,300
Alright.

74
00:03:23,480 --> 00:03:24,090
Thanks.

75
00:03:24,550 --> 00:03:24,900
You're welcome.

76
00:03:25,320 --> 00:03:25,810
Thank you, Mr. Fu.

77
00:03:25,920 --> 00:03:26,410
See you.

78
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:27,340
Okay.

79
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:28,850
Take care.

80
00:03:36,710 --> 00:03:37,460
Lin!

81
00:03:38,920 --> 00:03:39,530
Mr. Fu.

82
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:41,220
What brings you here?

83
00:03:41,990 --> 00:03:42,900
I've been listening for a while.

84
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:43,220
Come on,

85
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,180
let's chat inside.

86
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,370
Long time no see.

87
00:03:46,590 --> 00:03:47,340
Did you grow taller?

88
00:03:50,590 --> 00:03:51,060
Here, have some tea.

89
00:03:52,270 --> 00:03:53,650
Mr. Fu, I think
you should have some first.

90
00:03:54,200 --> 00:03:54,690
Otherwise, you won't

91
00:03:54,870 --> 00:03:56,340
be able to hold back the anger
stirred up by those parents.

92
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:00,530
You heard it all?

93
00:04:04,830 --> 00:04:05,410
I'm noticing

94
00:04:05,430 --> 00:04:06,740
this new batch of students

95
00:04:07,870 --> 00:04:08,940
is really impressive.

96
00:04:09,270 --> 00:04:11,090
They value truth and facts,

97
00:04:12,040 --> 00:04:13,410
stand up for themselves,

98
00:04:13,760 --> 00:04:14,620
and refuse to be wronged.

99
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:17,660
Kids these days

100
