221
00:07:49,830 --> 00:07:50,420
Jiao!

222
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:53,740
Jiao, are you okay?

223
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:56,130
I knew it was a misunderstanding.

224
00:07:57,590 --> 00:07:58,100
Auntie,

225
00:07:58,440 --> 00:07:59,300
what brings you here?

226
00:07:59,960 --> 00:08:01,210
It's fine, just a misunderstanding.

227
00:08:01,270 --> 00:08:01,980
No need to worry so much.

228
00:08:02,910 --> 00:08:04,180
Shiyun, you're always so considerate.

229
00:08:05,320 --> 00:08:06,770
Help me talk some sense into Jiao.

230
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:08,740
Classmates will always
have little disagreements.

231
00:08:08,910 --> 00:08:10,570
It's better to reduce
the trouble to a minimum,

232
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:11,060
right?

233
00:08:11,520 --> 00:08:12,130
After all,

234
00:08:12,230 --> 00:08:13,420
you're in Grade 12 now.

235
00:08:13,470 --> 00:08:14,500
Studies come first,

236
00:08:14,590 --> 00:08:15,180
right?

237
00:08:15,470 --> 00:08:16,100
Auntie, don't worry.

238
00:08:16,120 --> 00:08:16,860
I definitely will.

239
00:08:17,590 --> 00:08:18,060
Speaking of which,

240
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:20,450
Jiao, I'm really concerned about you.

241
00:08:20,760 --> 00:08:21,570
What's going on with you lately?

242
00:08:21,640 --> 00:08:22,570
Your grades have dropped again.

243
00:08:22,640 --> 00:08:23,860
You can't keep going on like this.

244
00:08:24,790 --> 00:08:25,540
Last time,

245
00:08:25,590 --> 00:08:26,450
you went home past midnight,

246
00:08:26,520 --> 00:08:27,210
and I covered for you.

247
00:08:27,270 --> 00:08:28,370
But honestly, I didn't feel…

248
00:08:28,710 --> 00:08:29,180
Wait.

249
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:32,380
She went home past midnight?

250
00:08:32,510 --> 00:08:32,970
No…

251
00:08:33,680 --> 00:08:34,090
Auntie,

252
00:08:34,510 --> 00:08:35,570
you didn't know about that?

253
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:36,570
Jiao,

254
00:08:37,040 --> 00:08:37,610
I'm sorry.

255
00:08:37,830 --> 00:08:38,330
- I…
- You…

256
00:08:38,590 --> 00:08:39,300
Enough.

257
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,420
You should leave now.

258
00:08:40,630 --> 00:08:41,300
Gu Xuejiao!

259
00:08:42,710 --> 00:08:43,490
Sorry, Shiyun.

260
00:08:43,630 --> 00:08:44,090
I need to talk

261
00:08:44,110 --> 00:08:45,210
to Xuejiao about something private.

262
00:08:45,750 --> 00:08:46,610
Why don't you head back first?

263
00:08:46,750 --> 00:08:47,900
Don't make your mom worry.

264
00:08:48,630 --> 00:08:48,970
Okay.

265
00:08:49,990 --> 00:08:50,940
I shouldn't have said anything.

266
00:08:51,320 --> 00:08:52,730
Auntie, please don't be mad.

267
00:08:52,870 --> 00:08:54,020
Xuejiao didn't mean it.

268
00:08:54,590 --> 00:08:55,330
I'll get going now.

269
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:56,490
You…!

270
00:08:56,590 --> 00:08:57,450
Gu Xuejiao,

271
00:08:58,160 --> 00:08:59,420
I knew you and Gu Mingze were

272
00:08:59,470 --> 00:09:00,420
up to no good.

273
00:09:00,870 --> 00:09:01,900
A girl your age,

274
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:03,020
staying out till
the middle of the night,

275
00:09:03,110 --> 00:09:03,970
what were you doing?

276
00:09:04,110 --> 00:09:05,060
Tell me the truth.

277
00:09:05,590 --> 00:09:06,060
Mom,

278
00:09:06,800 --> 00:09:07,900
just because Zhou Shiyun said something,

279
00:09:07,990 --> 00:09:08,940
you're going to scold me again,

280
00:09:08,990 --> 00:09:09,420
aren't you?

281
00:09:10,110 --> 00:09:10,970
I've got nothing to say.

282
00:09:13,160 --> 00:09:13,570
Fine.

283
00:09:14,230 --> 00:09:15,850
If you're so tough,
then don't come home!

284
00:09:25,710 --> 00:09:26,940
Honey, I might've

285
00:09:27,160 --> 00:09:28,140
gone too far just now

286
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:29,090
with what I said to Xuejiao.

287
00:09:29,160 --> 00:09:30,090
What should I do now?

288
00:09:32,470 --> 00:09:33,210
We're leaving.

289
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:33,730
Bye.

290
00:09:33,830 --> 00:09:34,210
Bye.

291
00:10:13,830 --> 00:10:14,490
What are you doing here?

292
00:10:32,590 --> 00:10:33,260
It's late.

293
00:10:33,510 --> 00:10:34,330
